    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has plenty of life left for its next owner! It runs smoothly, looks great, and is just waiting for a new home. I've taken good care of it, so you're getting a fantastic deal on a very dependable car. Drop me a message if you're interested\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
