      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-appointed interior, this specimen offers a refined driving experience and proven reliability. We invite you to inspect this exceptional automotive investment, which stands as a testament to diligent ownership and enduring quality.",
      "price": 34900.0,
