    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm selling my car and it is honestly in such great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for many more adventures. It drives super smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve priced it to move because I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
